title: Guy J Once In A Blue Moon
description:
Guy J returns to Bedrock with what is probably one of the most eagerly awaited releases of the year. Having been an outstanding highlight in his sets for many months, and been the subject to endless discussion across social media, Candyland is set to take things to another level. For many people around the world, Guy Js music is uniquely joyous, uplifting

02 - Candyland
